{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":108,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘青芷","listener":null,"text":"不用谢。","tone":"微笑","chapter":5,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"这件事，芮某确实不该……","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"恩公安健！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"他曾有恩于你？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"恩公曾救芮某一命。","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"所以他要求你来这里？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"你可知，他为何要你伪装？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":5,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"对这件事，芮某深感不解，不知恩公是何用意？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"他的用意确是深长！","tone":"无奈","chapter":5,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"是何用意？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"那他不应该不告诉你呀！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"倘若他此举对你不利呢？","tone":"无奈","chapter":5,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"芮某承他赐命，将不考虑！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"你一片好心，我代他谢谢你了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"芮某告辞了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"你可要小心一点！","tone":"担心","chapter":5,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"我却不知要如何小心？","tone":"微笑","chapter":5,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"我还是告诉你吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"你大概不知道简老夫人并不是召舞的亲生母亲，简伯父在世时曾有一位前妻，就是召舞的亲生母亲，当召舞生下时母亲便去世，简伯父后娶简老夫人，生下召稽与怀萱两兄妹，自幼召舞便和简老夫人不和，召舞性格冷僻，甚不得简老夫人的喜欢……","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"……等简伯父去世，他们母子俩表面无事，其实暗中勾心斗角，简老夫人恨不得置召舞于死地……","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"天下哪有这等残酷的后母！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":5,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"你或许不信，但召舞怕被他后母害死，才流浪在外，半年未回直到找着一个替身……","tone":"无奈","chapter":5,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"难道恩公的意思是要芮某代他一死？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"恩公不是她的对手？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":5,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"差得太远了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"那么姑娘，你呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_liu_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"刘育芷","listener":null,"text":"你以后要有什么事来这里找我，不要再到后山去叫我了……","tone":"低语","chapter":5,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","sp